Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.28,0:00:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.65,0:00:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Yui-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.97,0:00:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I left her a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.82,0:00:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine, just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.49,0:00:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.85,0:00:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Africa must be hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.25,0:00:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that young man still practice archery?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:01:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he's an archaeologist,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,so he's excavating.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.36,0:01:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,People meet one another, part,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and then meet again.{cf ep 6 - love one another}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Life is mysterious. You should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui-chan is old enough now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.06,0:02:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,that young man is an archaeologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.09,0:02:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to find a guide for tomorrow by taking lessons from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That proverb makes sense in martial arts as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The village may have sunk under the water,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but your home town will always be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.73,0:02:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back anytime you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.73,0:02:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.58,0:02:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
