Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.67,0:03:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.73,0:03:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui... -san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm thinking of resuming my life as a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please support me."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't... leave me alone.
