Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.26,0:04:16.06,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\pos(320,360)\b1\bord0\fs40\fnArtificeSSK\c&HD67467&\4c&H907276&\xshad-4\yshad3\be1}Spring for Everyone and . . .
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:28.28,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\fs25\an8}Sign: Yasohachi Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm really going to be your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my father and Misako-san are getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.53,0:04:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:04:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to the ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Africa is too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.69,0:05:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You called me out here just to ask that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If that was your question,\N why couldn't you ask it at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only you and me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the two of us are alone now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,some things are hard to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Narusawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen Makoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to know where Makoto is,\N it's fastest to ask Narusawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Some snob I know said that. I hate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Some snob?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.71,0:06:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Saionji Aritomo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, that particular snob was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. I knocked over the old man's valuable books.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Onii-chan's fault for leaving them there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The first time I met...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yui-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your look of ennui is also beautiful.{WTF he's really saying "ennui"}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.25,0:09:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Saionji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, stop it, Yui-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me Aritomo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A-ri-to-mo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We spent a night together in a mountain cottage, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're acting a bit distant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Nothing happened between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.31,0:09:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling embarrassed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes me feel embarrassed too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,When I remember our intense hug that night...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I got carried away just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot that I have someone with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.52,0:09:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When I went to your house,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:10:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,he forced his way into the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked me to drive all over the place.{acchi kocchi!}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He was very annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm quite tolerant, so it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it were someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you were embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When you suddenly ran out of the cottage,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised, Yui-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.02,0:10:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But from the helicopter,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,we saw that silvery-white scene, shining under the rising sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like going to a magical world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, remembering that now makes me feel warm inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It was very moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What... do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, right. I wanted to borrow your bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Yui-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, but can you take me home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:11.71,Overlap,,0,0,0,,You were finally in my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you let Aritomo\N take you home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take Yui-san home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This car has a very comfortable ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of the best in the Saionji classic car collection,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can assure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.64,0:11:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the elegant form.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Its shape is handcrafted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.51,0:11:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You can feel the warmth and softness emanating from every part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watching it makes my heart tighten with joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I wonder what's wrong with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.49,0:12:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it seems there's no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They've broken up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, this makes me feel happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Break-ing-up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So I end up in the water today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.45,0:13:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.22,0:13:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here to ask me out on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.56,0:13:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm training for the next archery competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.04,0:14:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get my revenge there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.42,0:14:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm giving up my vacations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I can't go out on a date for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:17.10,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(40,0)\pos(322,307.5)\bord0\frz-6.2\fax0.1\c&HCFCCC3&\fs34\fnFelt\fsp2}Career Guidance Office
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:21.02,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(322,307)\bord0\frz-6.2\fax0.1\c&HCFCCC3&\fs34\fnFelt\fsp2}Career Guidance Office
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Narusawa-san, I hope you do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you'll be able to pass the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were a typical{she's saying "naive"} girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but you've chosen an unexpected course.{future}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.73,0:15:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kondou-kun, you don't seem to be doing well these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.24,0:15:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,When are you going to decide about your future?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My mom and your dad are getting married soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.71,0:16:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to say something, say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,S-So...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you're really going to skip the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.96,0:16:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:45.54,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\fs25\an8\fad(600,1400)}Sign: Yasohachi Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.38,0:18:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kondou Makoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.89,0:19:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is my last high school competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to support me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.87,0:19:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you're coming,\N everything will be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,See you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.95,0:19:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:37.69,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25\fad(600,0)}Paper: Evaluation for Studying Abroad\N Accepted
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Narusawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.85,0:19:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-san, do you still like ohagi{a rice ball coated with sweetened red beans}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.85,0:19:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\an8}Note: Ohagi are rice balls coated with sweetened red beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:20:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember when I transferred here? I was so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.44,0:20:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the first person who spoke to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.76,0:20:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It made me feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That time, you asked me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"Do you like ohagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to have some with me after school?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.14,0:20:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And we ate enough for nine people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The person working at the shop was flabbergasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.04,0:20:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}do{\fscx150\i0} {\r}remember that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I still like ohagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't eat as much anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a nice memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It was cheap, and the portions were large and tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's why that shop closed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.91,0:20:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I hope you do well at tomorrow's competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.66,0:20:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:20:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:20:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yui-san's studying abroad?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.93,0:21:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's leaving on a plane tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.38,0:21:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Something so important...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.89,0:21:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:25.38,Default,sign,0,0,0,,{\fs25\an8\fad(40,0)}Paper: Evaluation for Studying Abroad\NAccepted
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't she tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.39,0:21:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're not reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.80,0:21:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm not reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.18,0:21:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But my love for her is boundless!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.57,0:21:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a concise summary of a huge misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.02,0:21:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.91,0:21:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My love is a huge misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.88,0:21:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.60,0:21:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know when to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.17,0:21:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.31,0:22:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I never know when to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.25,0:22:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh oh. I have a bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:18.27,Default,sign,30,0,10,,{\fad(0,400)\an7\fs25}Sign: Career\NGuidance Office
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.16,0:22:20.98,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.00,0:22:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}am{\i0}... reliable!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.99,0:22:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My love is... {\i1}not{\i0\fscx150} {\r}a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.91,0:22:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you get it, you moron?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.49,0:22:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, does he know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.56,0:22:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not talking to each other right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.62,0:23:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they've sort of collapsed as a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.73,0:23:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.94,0:23:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,tomorrow is Shinohara Izumi's archery competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.05,0:23:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kondou promised he'd be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.42,0:23:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And where did you take those pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.53,0:23:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,From the garden of Kondou-kun's house, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.62,0:23:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You even stoop to trespassing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.62,0:23:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shame on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.77,0:23:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.88,0:23:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.78,0:24:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.57,0:24:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Onii-chan, wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.61,0:24:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.66,0:24:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.45,0:24:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.73,0:24:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Share it with Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.42,0:24:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to support her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.00,0:24:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope she wins the title.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.82,0:24:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll win the title, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.98,0:24:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.92,0:24:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye... Onii-chan.
